<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><meta name="theme-color" content="#080d18"><title>Limpar cache — JB3D Vendas</title><style>body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;display:grid;place-items:center;background:#080d18;color:#f4f7fb;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,sans-serif;padding:24px}.card{max-width:440px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #253149;border-radius:22px;background:#101827;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 20px 60px #0008}.icon{font-size:38px}.spin{width:28px;height:28px;border:3px solid #ffffff22;border-top-color:#38e8c6;border-radius:50%;animation:s .7s linear infinite;margin:18px auto}@keyframes s{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}small{color:#93a1b8;line-height:1.5}</style></head><body><div class="card"><div class="icon">🧹</div><h1>Limpando a versão antiga</h1><div class="spin"></div><p id="status">Removendo cache e instalação anterior…</p><small>Você será redirecionado automaticamente.</small></div><script>(async()=>{try{if('serviceWorker'in navigator){const regs=await navigator.serviceWorker.getRegistrations();await Promise.all(regs.map(r=>r.unregister()));}if('caches'in window){const keys=await caches.keys();await Promise.all(keys.map(k=>caches.delete(k)));}localStorage.setItem('jb3d_cache_cleaned_v24',new Date().toISOString());document.getElementById('status').textContent='Cache limpo. Abrindo o aplicativo…';setTimeout(()=>location.replace('./index.html?v=2.4.0&limpo='+Date.now()),900);}catch(e){document.getElementById('status').textContent='Não foi possível limpar automaticamente. Abra o site em uma aba anônima.';}})();</script></body></html>